room_title: Escape room "Trapped in a Room with a Zombie" by Great Room Escape in Cincinnati
room_address: 4814 Peter Pl, West Chester Township, OH 45246
room_description: There is one hungry zombie chained to the wall. Every five minutes a buzzer sounds and the chain grows a foot from the wall! In 60 minutes the zombie will be able to reach you, so you have to find the ultimate key to freedom or join the walking dead!
